On April 19, 2021, we denied your request for expedited processing of your I-765, Application for Employment Authorization, Receipt Number WAC2190039474.  We do not believe, based on a review of your request, that your case meets one or more of the expedite criteria and otherwise merits expedited processing. We review all expedite requests on a case-by-case basis, and we grant them at the discretion of the director.  Information regarding the USCIS expedite policy, including the expedite criteria, is available at www.uscis.gov/forms/expedite-criteria. We review all expedite requests on a case-by-case basis, and we grant them at the discretion of the director. checking USCIS for Reciept: WAC2190041078
On August 2, 2021, we denied your request for expedited processing of your I-765, Application for Employment Authorization, Receipt Number WAC2190041078.  We do not believe, based on a review of your request, that your case meets one or more of the expedite criteria and otherwise merits expedited processing. We review all expedite requests on a case-by-case basis, and we grant them at the discretion of the director.  Information regarding the USCIS expedite policy, including the expedite criteria, is available at www.uscis.gov/forms/expedite-criteria.  If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.

Information regarding the USCIS expedite policy, including the expedite criteria, is available at www.uscis.gov/forms/expedite-criteria.  If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.

On June 23, 2021, we denied your request for expedited processing of your I-765, Application for Employment Authorization, Receipt Number WAC2190042013.  We do not believe, based on a review of your request, that your case meets one or more of the expedite criteria and otherwise merits expedited processing. Information regarding the USCIS expedite policy, including the expedite criteria, is available at www.uscis.gov/forms/expedite-criteria. We review all expedite requests on a case-by-case basis, and we grant them at the discretion of the director.  Information regarding the USCIS expedite policy, including the expedite criteria, is available at www.uscis.gov/forms/expedite-criteria.
